There has been at least a five ''Aquila'' coin in use as [[Imperium of Mankind|Imperial]] currency in the time prior to the [[Horus Heresy]].{{Fn|11a}}

===Horus Heresy===
Towards the end of the [[Horus Heresy]] when the final battle for [[Mars]] was underway the [[Power Armour|armour]] development teams were evacuated from Mars to [[Terra]] where they continued their work. The result of their work was the [[Power_Armour#Mark_7_.22Aquila_.28Imperator.2C_Eagle.29_Armour.22|Mark 7]] ''Armorum Impetor'' or ''Eagle Armour'' which takes its common name from the ''Eagle'' device it bears. The ''Eagle Armour'' started to reach the loyalist [[Space Marine]] defenders on Terra and on the Moon when [[Horus]] and his forces overcame the last resistance on Mars.{{Fn|26}} For possible uses of the ''Aquila'' on earlier marks see {{Fn|Note 2}}.

