{{OrksPortal}}{{ImperiumPortal}}
'''Black Markets''' are hidden criminal underground markets, that deal in the rarest and most dangerous of goods, especially those that have been outlawed by the [[Imperium]].{{Fn|1}}

At their most mundane, a Black Market might offer pilfered [[Enforcer]] and [[PDF|Militia]] weaponry, chems or even rare wargear. At their more esoteric, they may sell strange [[Xenos]] weaponry and creatures brought in via the [[Cold Trade]] or even objects imbued with the [[Warp]].{{Fn|1}}

[[Gretchin]] are also known to operate their own type of Black Market, within their [[Ork]] dominated society. This includes selling fungus-beer, roasting [[squig]]s on sticks, coordinating the bets when a fight breaks out or looting corpses for fun and profit.{{Fn|2}}

