{{ImperiumPortal}}
The '''{{PAGENAME}}''' are an armed force of the [[Adeptus Astra Telepathica]], having been active since the [[Great Crusade]] and [[Horus Heresy]].{{Fn|1}}{{Fn|2}} 

Black Sentinels provide security for [[Astropath]]s and their facilities across the [[Sol System]] and beyond. They are also entrusted with the task of eliminating compromised [[Psyker]]s, prowling across the gantries and corridors of the [[Adeptus Astra Telepathica|Telepathica]] headquarters on [[Terra]], forever poised for the first twitch or spasm of possession. Well-trained and armed with [[Lasgun]]s, they are dressed in black armor and wear masks that resemble snarling beasts.{{Fn|1}}{{Fn|2}}

