{{ImperiumPortal}}
'''Chiromancers''' are [[Imperial]] [[Psykers]], who have been medically and psychically trained to treat victims of [[Warp]]-born diseases.{{Fn|1}} 

Despite their skills, however, those given to their care, suffer from maladies of the soul and body, which few survive. Due to the nature of their work, Chiromancers serve aboard [[Isolation Ship]]s and wear [[Hazard Suit]]s, while treating their patients. By doing this, the [[Imperium]] limits the risk of any Warp disease spreading and endangering its worlds. High ranking members of the Chiromancer order, are known as '''Chiromancer-Captains'''.{{Fn|1}}

