'''Dacatarai''' is an aggressive [[Imperial]] fighting style, that is ideal for countering hordes of foes.{{Fn|1}} 
==Description==
Its users can effortlessly managing their foes' ebb and flow, to prevent themselves from being overwhelmed. The [[Adeptus Custodes]] also practice Dacatarai, as part of their [[Adeptus Custodes#Martial Ka'tah Fighting Styles|Martial Ka'tah]]s, though it has been modified for their use{{Fn|1}}. The Custodes of the [[Dread Host]] are known to specialize in using Dacatarai in battle.{{Fn|2}}

