{{Ambig|subject=the animal|disambiguation=Dog}}
'''Dogs''' are quadruped mammals native to [[Terra]] but encountered on several other worlds throughout the [[Imperium]]. They are popular domestic pets.{{Fn|1a}}

The [[Iron Snakes]] [[Space Marine Chapter]] is unique among the [[Adeptus Astartes]] in that they are trained to use dogs, whose senses are useful in tracking and flushing out [[Dark Eldar]].{{Fn|1b}}

Dogs are also genetically related to wolves. Hence, after the [[Burning of Prospero]], it was customary for [[Chaos Space Marines]] of the [[Thousand Sons]] [[Legion]] to refer to the [[Space Wolves]] as "the Dogs."{{Fn|2}}

