{{ImperiumPortal}} The '''Feast of the Primarch's Rebirth''' is a recently created [[Imperial]] celebration, that honors the return of the reborn [[Primarch]] [[Roboute Guilliman]] to the Imperium. It is traditional to commemorate this celebration with fasting, ruthless self-flagellation, and marathon [[Ecclesiarchy]] litany sessions.{{Fn|1}}
==Sources== *{{Endn|1}}: [https://regimental-standard.com/2020/04/08/the-great-egg-hunt/ Regimental Standard: The Great 'Egg' Hunt! (Posted on 08/04/2020)] (Last accessed on 8 April 2020)
[[Category:Celebrations]] [[Category:Ecclesiarchy]] [[Category:Ultramarines]] [[Category:Imperium]]

{{ImperiumPortal}}
The '''Festival of the Heart''' is an [[Imperial]] festival, that is rumored to date back to old [[Terra]].{{Fn|1}} 

Little is known about this tradition, except that it involves greeting each other with Happy Festival of the Heart, knowing the precise anatomical location of the heart and some notions of fraternity. Because of this, the [[Astra Militarum]] produces motivational cards along these lines, so that [[Guardsmen]] can give them to each other, their [[Commissar]]s and the enemies of the Imperium.{{Fn|1}}

==Trivia==
The Festival of the Heart is an in-universe equivalent of Valentine's Day.{{Fn|1}}

