{{ImperiumPortal}}
'''House Farwell''' was an [[Imperial]] mercantile clan active on [[Armageddon]], based out of [[Hive Helsreach]].{{Fn|1}}

They are known to have possessed a private armed security force known as the [[House Farwellian Constabulary]]. This, however, did not save them in the [[Third War for Armageddon]]; when the [[ork]]s [[Helsreach Crusade|invaded]] Helsreach, the presence of several hundred armed Constabularies protecting the House's estates proved an irresistible lure for the greenskins. Seeking a good scrap, the orks overran the Farwellian estate and butchered the Imperials present to the last man.{{Fn|1}}

