{{ImperiumPortal}}
'''House Tarracine''' was an [[Imperial]] mercantile clan active on [[Armageddon]], based out of [[Hive Helsreach]].{{Fn|1}}

The House's estate was destroyed by the [[ork]]s when they [[Helsreach Crusade|invaded]] Helsreach during the [[Third War for Armageddon]]. However, thanks to an expertly-orchestrated defence, seven members of House Tarracine survived the attack; these scions of Tarracine, along with the House as a whole, were left in a strong position compared to the other mercantiles of Helsreach when the time came to rebuild the city following the invasion.{{Fn|1}}

