{{ImperiumPortal}}
'''Imperial Regent''', sometimes called '''Lord Regent''' or the '''Regent of [[Terra]]''' is a title in the [[Imperium]] used several times throughout history.

Extremely prestigious, it is second only to the [[Emperor]] in authority. Its holder is said to be the living voice of the Emperor.{{Fn|3}} The title sometimes overlaps with [[Lord Commander of the Imperium]], but presumably includes civic authority as well as military. The title was one of the few positions that warranted the placement of members of the [[Adeptus Custodes]] as bodyguards. The post was presumably created after the Emperor of Mankind withdrew from the [[Great Crusade]], and the administration of Terra in general, to work on his own [[Webway Project|secret projects]].{{Fn|5}}

