{{ImperiumPortal}} The '''Inspectorate of Shipping'''{{Fn|1a}} is an [[Imperial]] organization charged with investigating the [[Merchant Fleets]] whenever major irregularities in scheduling or shipping occur{{Fn|1b}}. Field agents known as '''Inspectors''' are sent in person to investigate these occurrences, and wear a coat as a standard uniform{{Fn|1c}} and are issued a [[laspistol]] with which to defend themselves{{Fn|1d}}. These agents have the power to go wherever their investigation takes them and even offer Inspectorate confidentiality agreements, within limits, in order to solve their cases{{Fn|1a}}. In practice, however, there are certain areas of the [[Speaker for the Chartist Captains]]' [[Nexus Axiomaticâ€Ž]] fortress that are deemed to be off-limits to outsiders. Any Inspector who attempts to enter them will be met by the armed [[Praeses Mercatura]] and told the Inspectorate of Shipping has no jurisdiction in those areas.{{Fn|1b}}
