{{ImperiumPortal}}
The '''Logos Historica Verita''' is a new governmental department of [[Roboute Guilliman]]'s reformed [[Imperium]]. Roboute Guilliman awoke in late [[M41]] to find that the Imperium's 10,000 year history was catalogued in an extremely unreliable, secretive, and often contradictory fashion. He created the Logos as a means to rectify this problem and create the first true reliable history of the Imperium.{{Fn|1}}

The Logos is made up of hundreds of skilled scholars and historians, hand-picked by Guilliman, and chosen for their more liberal views of historiography. The Logos' objectives and policies stand in stark contrast to the [[Ordo Chronos]], which has turned to [[Chronostrife|violence]] in response to Guilliman's reformations.{{Fn|1}}

As of [[M42]], the Logos is estimated to operate around 500 men and women.{{Fn|1}}

