'''Ploin''' are a type of fruit known to be grown on a number of [[Imperial]] worlds (including multiple planets in the [[Calixis Sector]] and the [[Koronus Expanse]]{{Fn|2}}, along with the planet [[Tanith]] before its destruction{{Fn|1}}).{{Fn|2}}
Each ploin has green skin, pink flesh and black pips.{{Fn|1}} They are often brewed into a non-alcoholic beverage popular with many explorers as it is nutrient-rich, capable of combating many common illnesses brought on by the habitual poor diets inherent to extended space travel.{{Fn|2}}
When cheaply fermented, ploins produce a clear, strong drink commonly known as '''"wobble"''' â€” as this is both what the fruit does when set upright, as well as what most users do after imbibing.{{Fn|2}}
