A '''Recidivist''' is the general [[Imperial]] term for [[Humans]] who break the laws of the Imperium{{Fn|1}} or oppose its rule.{{Fn|2}}{{Fn|3}} 

These include [[Imperial]] crime lords, slavers, fencers, fixers{{Fn|1}} and those citizens who commit or preach sedition against the Imperium{{Fn|2}}. The term is also applied to [[Human]]s of non-Imperial worlds, who resist the Imperium's efforts to bring [[Compliance]] to their Homeworlds.{{Fn|3}}

