{{ImperiumPortal}}
The '''Sangua-Terran War Council''' is a [[Gorandahl Sub-sector]] coalition of military and religious leaders, that was formed to stabilize the [[Sub-sector]] in the wake of the [[Great Rift]]'s creation.{{Fn|1}}  
==History==
It was created by [[Imperial Commander]] [[Kalendela Tol]] and aided the remaining [[Imperial]] [[System]]s of the [[Gorandahl Sub-sector]], until contact with the wider Imperium was made. Bitter years of warfare followed, but the [[Sub-sector]] became relatively stable. The later discovery of the [[Nachmund Gauntlet]] would make Gorandahl's safety a priority for the Imperium and it became used to send supplies to the important world of [[Vigilus]]. The Council, though, became overstretched as they complied with their new orders, while also protecting the Sub-sector from the Imperium's enemies. Word has now spread, however, that [[Abaddon the Despoiler]] has now [[Nachmund Rift War|sent his forces down]] the Nachmund Gauntlet and the [[Heretics]] would soon fall upon Gorandahl.{{Fn|1}} 

