The '''Ten Truths Syndicate''' is a [[Heretical]] [[Imperial]] [[Criminal Cartel]]{{Fn|1c}}, that is active in the [[Macharian Sector]] and is rumored to have ties across many of its worlds.{{Fn|1b}}
==Description==
They are utterly pragmatic and atheistic, the Syndicate is willing to work with anyone, including [[Chaos Cultists]] and [[Xenos]], as long as they are paid to do so. In functionality, the Syndicate is a similar to a secret society, as new layers of truths are revealed to its members when they progress up the [[Cartel]]'s ranks.{{Fn|1c}}
