{{ImperiumPortal}} The '''War of the False Primarch''' was a dark and bloody episode of the [[Imperium]]'s history, now largely lost to myth and purged from all records, that plunged the [[Segmentum Pacificus]] into anarchy from 780.[[M33]] to 860.M33. The conflict was finally ended when the [[High Lords of Terra]], conveyed the [[Pentarchy of Blood]] and tasked five loyal [[Chapters]] to destroy eleven others, that had been declared [[Excommunicate Traitoris|Traitoris Perdita]] for their actions during the war.{{Fn|1}}
==Source== *{{Endn|1}}: [[Imperial Armour Volume Two - Second Edition]] pg. 17
