The '''Wraithbone Phoenix''' is a legendary treasure hidden somewhere within [[Alecto (Hive World)|Alecto]]'s sprawling [[Hive City]] [[Varangantua]]. It is currently being sought after by the thieves [[Baggit]] and [[Clodde]], who need it to pay off their debts and save their lives.{{Fn|1}}
