'''Xeno-Narcotic''' is the [[Imperial]] term for [[Narcotics]] that have [[Xenos]] origins, but are still used by [[Humans]].{{Fn|1}} ==Description== The substances are illegal for [[Imperial]]s to [[Cold Trade|possess]] and those who are caught doing so by the [[Adeptus Arbites]], will be put on trial for the crime. Should they be found guilty by the Arbites' adjudicators, the offenders could be sentenced to death.{{Fn|1}}
==Sources== *{{Endn|1}}: [[Messiah Complex (Short Story)]] - [[Deathwatch: The Long Vigil (Anthology)]]
