{{ImperiumPortal}}
'''Xenology''' is the [[Imperial]] study of [[Xenos]]. Those individuals who study xenology are known as '''Xenologists'''.{{Fn|1}}

The science has had a chequered history, however, and has been described as either [[Human|humanity's]] greatest hope or its greatest folly. There is no formal training to become a Xenologist, though practitioners will need to have the resources required to carry out their work.{{Fn|1}}

